  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: App crashes if try to record audio while microphone access was denied.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nApp does not crash. Instructions on how to enable microphone access are shown\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nApp crashes if press and hold microphone icon to record audio in Instabug report. Note that there is popup \"Microphone access denied\" shown but as soon as finger is released app crashes.\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\nVideo: https://drive.google.com/open?id=0Bz3t9zSg1wb7UENTcGNXVFBOQlE\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Shake phone\r\n- Report a problem \r\n- Tap -> in top right corner to proceed to next screen\r\n- Tap on + in the bottom \r\n- Tap on record a voice note. \r\n- Tap on microphone icon. As a result, popup to allow access to microphone is shown\r\n- Don't allow access to microphone\r\n- Tap again on microphone icon and hold a finger on it \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: 0.9.7d38\r\n* Operating System: iOS only\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n[StatusIm-2017-05-03-140603.crash.txt](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/973206/StatusIm-2017-05-03-140603.crash.txt)\r\n",
